text: The best weekend of golf of the year. Augusta is golf's field of dreams Hale Irwin once said about The Masters golf tournament that "you start to choke at The Masters when you drive through the front gate." Dave Marr said "at my first Masters, I got the feeling that if I didnt

play well, I wouldn't go to heaven." Gary Player said "every shot is within a fraction of disaster. That's what makes it so great." This weekend some of us forget about ODTE options, investor sentiment, FAANG and interest rates. Some of us just watch golf. @ferrotv @Tomkeene
